opinion:
510 U.S. 1008

In re Disbarment of Boyne.
No. D-1334.

Supreme Court of United States.

December 6, 1993.

1

It is ordered that Gilbert Wentworth Boyne, of Modesto, Cal., be suspended from the practice of law in this Court and that a rule issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
